extendedInfo.description: Get 3 free ringtones! And listen to 250 unique tones from our popular 2500 Funny Ringtones app. Examples include:"Warning! An idiot is calling.""That smoking hot babe with the long legs is calling. You better pick up!""Miss High Maintenance is calling you...AGAIN!""Your ex-wife is calling. Time to hit the ignore button, isn't it?!""Your boyfriend is calling. Well, aren't you the lucky one!"...and thousands more!Quickly scroll through the list of tones. Touch a tone name to listen to a short preview. If you like what you hear, download the entire tone -- up to 30 seconds each.Install the sounds as ringtones or Android notifications. Works with just the click of a button.Note: To download ringtones, you must have access to your wireless provider's data network, or Wi-Fi, or another Internet connection source.
